<plot>"Ana's Chronotope" is an experimental meditation on writing and the process of remembrance embodied by the words and experiences of Ana, the main character of this film. To make sense of her abusive past in the isolated environs of rural Texas, an Asian-American woman reads a script written by her stepfather.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?037736</url></doc>
